  "body": "### Description\nTo enable the validator client to perform sync committee duties, update the beacon node REST API (and `ValidatorApiChannel`) to expose the following functions:\n\n* Calculate and return sync committee duties for a set of validators\n* Support subscribing to sync committee subnet (including updating ENR). Needs to be scheduled to subscribe at a specific epoch (before the start of the sync committee period) and terminate at the end of the relevant sync committee period\n* Produce a sync committee signature? Might be able to do this just by getting the current head from existing API?\n* Publish a sync committee signature to the appropriate subnet\n* Create a SyncCommitteeContribution aggregating all sync committee signatures matching a given block root\n* Publish SignedContributionAndProof\n\nProposed APIs: https://hackmd.io/@QYHAVYiHRg65pdI_CEm7Eg/syncommitteeapi",
